Text:
Had the complete Amazon track listing.  Cheb Khaled - Alech Taadi (Alaach Taadi) is not included. This is not included in the OST anyway.

It can be found by the original owner of the song Khaled on his N'ssi N'ssi album. A torrent of the album (and others) can be found here:

https://thepiratebay.sx/torrent/5833844/Khaled_-_Best_of
